name: FedEx McDonnell Douglas MD-11F [N602FE] Close Up Taxi at LAX ᴴᴰ
description:
MD-11! :D :D :D You can probably imagine the look of sheer joy  on my face when I saw this bird taxiing ;) 

Here is one of FedEx's beautiful MD-11s taxiing from the maintenance area (I think) to the cargo ramp. Just listen to those CF-6s humming, and watch how it "climbs" over 2 runways to get to its destination! Hope you enjoy, and watch in 1080p!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
